Base.FunctionName: Delete: All but the matching characters
Base.FunctionDescription: Delete all characters from the name if the character is not found as one of the specified characters. Example: abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz.

Base.FunctionName: Shorten name: Convert to first N
Base.FunctionDescription: Convert the name to the first N characters of the name. If the name does not contain N characters, it is not changed.
